ze:14px;line-height:34px;;">园区外企党委积极策划</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">7月1日下午</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">在圆融天幕东街举办了</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">以“不忘初心 砥砺前行”为主题的</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">迎七一党建知识竞赛总决赛</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.6675" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dtKt6iawKSvmlia54qgDdUJic00dGgzHzd01nP9FE9lcVHic5Mp9jFjnGXHh532lK7EpHuwE03wLfNhyD1sBECIQqA/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="800"></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">园区党工委委员、组织部部长林小明，园区经发委主任、外企党委书记孙扬澄及共建单位园区海关党组成员、副关长、机关党委书记李永江等出席活动并颁奖，同时吸引了近200名外企党员前来观战。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">本次比赛是由外企党委下属11个片区组队参加，采取“线上与线下”相结合的方式，预赛通过线上答题，创新的比赛形式也极大的提高了党员的参与度。通过预赛和半决赛的层层选拔，最终脱颖而出的五个片区与共建单位海关稽查处支部，共六支代表队进入到本次总决赛。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.562962962962963" data-s="300,640" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dtKt6iawKSvmlia54qgDdUJic00dGgzHzd0E33fia2NTC6IQCFnmsXfQFnpUqsQsFog7AIb79dLZHab11CHVry8Crw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080"></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">总决赛内容新颖，趣味性十足，包含了新党章、十九大报告、习近平讲话系列、红色歌曲、红色电影、“两学一做”平台线上学习内容等。设置了必答题、抢答题、记忆题、风险题四个环节。在决赛现场，参赛队员配合默契，沉着应答，比分紧咬不下，精彩的表现向大家展示了新时期共产党员的风采。随后啦啦队的最强大脑、最佳拍档、最美歌声等互动环节，将赛场氛围推向顶点，整个比赛过程气氛热烈、精彩纷呈。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: justify;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.6675" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dtKt6iawKSvmlia54qgDdUJic00dGgzHzd0qIav1OiaicS9eA4o3H8NzYYhsEGVOUKQ3MAhrXibKjqmQBTYzY70GdB5A/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="800"></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">经过激烈的角逐，由华润万家党委和松下研发党总支带领的第十片区获得一等奖及最佳片区组织奖，第八片区、第九、六、二片区分获二、三等奖，海关稽查处支部获得最佳协作奖。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: justify;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" data-s="300,640" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dtKt6iawKSvmlia54qgDdUJic00dGgzHzd05wK2MRuLaicvhLmDs0TPHJRdZCOuaoKQMDiceqsxwTiaQjpxDr2jvau6Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080"></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.562962962962963" data-s="300,640" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dtKt6iawKSvmlia54qgDdUJic00dGgzHzd0tGiaYW9DBHRQCpNcGAXCyVrceoLNlOCVatLqibRQrbnyNbrib26epMowQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080"></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">此次竞赛把枯燥的理论知识和活泼的比赛形式结合起来，激发了广大外企党员学习党建知识的热情，并将这份热情充分融入到党员的工作中去，学的更全面、做的更扎实，不断从合格走向优秀，用实际行动让党员风采在外企绽放。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: justify;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.6675" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dtKt6iawKSvmlia54qgDdUJic00dGgzHzd0nF4X9Inq9PKMYcJLVeutuBd4aHDDbaJnqGuAVTh2RCCN029h2B97dA/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="800"></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: justify;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">据悉，本次参赛的11个片区是由外企党委将所辖243家企业按照地域相邻、优势引领的原则划分而成的，分别由11名党委委员分片负责，积极推动党委、党总支引领党支部、党员数多带领党员数少的支部联合开展活动的区域化共建机制，实现了党组织活动的常态化和全覆盖。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" data-s="300,640" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/dtKt6iawKSvmlia54qgDdUJic00dGgzHzd0SSwsj4yJ0ArWcNnGVicpKiac7zxEW8OomchGP47iaEBQicE1VMET3LlbwA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080"></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">今年以来，园区外企党委按照中央、省市委和园区党工委的部署要求，围绕园区“党建引领工程”，积极打造“先锋惠企——外企党建服务联盟”品牌，着力解决外企党建发展不平衡的难题。主要做了如下工作：</span></p><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="92283" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="_135editor" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="#d9192b" data-custom="#d9192b"><section style="padding: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 100%;text-align: center;" data-width="100%"><section style="display: inline-block;padding-right: 15px;padding-left: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: -webkit-flex;font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;background-color: rgb(217, 25, 43);margin-bottom: -4px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);padding: 5px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 35px;padding-right: 5px;padding-left: 5px;border-right: 1px solid rgb(254, 254, 254);box-sizing: border-box;"><p class="135brush autonum" data-brushtype="text" data-original-title="" title="">1</p></section><section><section style="padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p class="135brush" data-brushtype="text"><span style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;letter-spacing: 2px;">健全党建工作领导体制。</span></p></section></section></section><section data-width="100%" style="width: 100%;height: 25px;background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvmlia54qgDdUJic00dGgzHzd0ibhuZ3DPGqroGrbYTfMHOPB1Mt5JPd8UdQP8vUkweJb53EicF1icSYjOg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);background-size: 100%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: right center;"><br  /></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">规范党委会议、基层书记例会等工作会议制度，完善党建工作目标管理责任制。落实党委委员工作责任，加强对党建片区的工作督导、对基层党建工作点的联系指导。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="92283" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="_135editor" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="#d9192b" data-custom="#d9192b"><section style="padding: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 100%;text-align: center;" data-width="100%"><section style="display: inline-block;padding-right: 15px;padding-left: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: -webkit-flex;font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;background-color: rgb(217, 25, 43);margin-bottom: -4px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);padding: 5px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 35px;padding-right: 5px;padding-left: 5px;border-right: 1px solid rgb(254, 254, 254);box-sizing: border-box;"><p class="135brush autonum" data-brushtype="text" data-original-title="" title="" data-num="2">2</p></section><section><section style="padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p class="135brush" data-brushtype="text"><span style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;letter-spacing: 2px;">打造“先锋惠企”党建品牌</span></p></section></section></section><section data-width="100%" style="width: 100%;height: 25px;background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvmlia54qgDdUJic00dGgzHzd0ibhuZ3DPGqroGrbYTfMHOPB1Mt5JPd8UdQP8vUkweJb53EicF1icSYjOg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);background-size: 100%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: right center;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">精心制定党建品牌建设和工作方案，依托党建片区和三星半导体党委等优势党组织，组建“外企党建服务联盟”。引导帮助各外企党组织围绕主品牌建设子品牌，形成外企党建品牌群。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="92283" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="_135editor" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="#d9192b" data-custom="#d9192b"><section style="padding: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 100%;text-align: center;" data-width="100%"><section style="display: inline-block;padding-right: 15px;padding-left: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: -webkit-flex;font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;background-color: rgb(217, 25, 43);margin-bottom: -4px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);padding: 5px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 35px;padding-right: 5px;padding-left: 5px;border-right: 1px solid rgb(254, 254, 254);box-sizing: border-box;"><p class="135brush autonum" data-brushtype="text" data-original-title="" title="" data-num="3">3</p></section><section><section style="padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p class="135brush" data-brushtype="text"><span style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;letter-spacing: 2px;">规范“三会一课”基本制度</span></p></section></section></section><section data-width="100%" style="width: 100%;height: 25px;background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvmlia54qgDdUJic00dGgzHzd0ibhuZ3DPGqroGrbYTfMHOPB1Mt5JPd8UdQP8vUkweJb53EicF1icSYjOg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);background-size: 100%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: right center;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">督促各基层组织按时规范开展“三会一课”、组织生活会、民主评议各项活动，严肃基层党内政治生活，克服组织弱化现象。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="92283" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="_135editor" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="#d9192b" data-custom="#d9192b"><section style="padding: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 100%;text-align: center;" data-width="100%"><section style="display: inline-block;padding-right: 15px;padding-left: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: -webkit-flex;font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;background-color: rgb(217, 25, 43);margin-bottom: -4px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);padding: 5px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 35px;padding-right: 5px;padding-left: 5px;border-right: 1px solid rgb(254, 254, 254);box-sizing: border-box;"><p class="135brush autonum" data-brushtype="text" data-original-title="" title="" data-num="4">4</p></section><section><section style="padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p class="135brush" data-brushtype="text"><span style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;letter-spacing: 2px;">强化党员教育管理工作</span></p></section></section></section><section data-width="100%" style="width: 100%;height: 25px;background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvmlia54qgDdUJic00dGgzHzd0ibhuZ3DPGqroGrbYTfMHOPB1Mt5JPd8UdQP8vUkweJb53EicF1icSYjOg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);background-size: 100%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: right center;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">围绕学习十九大精神、“学讲话、悟初心”主题党日活动，开展系列学习，实现党员教育常态化。完善党员动态管理机制，增强党员关怀力度。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><br  /></p><section class="_135editor" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="92283" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="_135editor" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: initial;box-sizing: border-box;" data-color="#d9192b" data-custom="#d9192b"><section style="padding: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 100%;text-align: center;" data-width="100%"><section style="display: inline-block;padding-right: 15px;padding-left: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: -webkit-flex;font-size:18px;line-height:38px;;background-color: rgb(217, 25, 43);margin-bottom: -4px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);padding: 5px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 35px;padding-right: 5px;padding-left: 5px;border-right: 1px solid rgb(254, 254, 254);box-sizing: border-box;"><p class="135brush autonum" data-brushtype="text" data-original-title="" title="" data-num="5">5</p></section><section><section style="padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;"><p class="135brush" data-brushtype="text"><span style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;letter-spacing: 2px;">创新基层组织活动方式</span></p></section></section></section><section data-width="100%" style="width: 100%;height: 25px;background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/dtKt6iawKSvmlia54qgDdUJic00dGgzHzd0ibhuZ3DPGqroGrbYTfMHOPB1Mt5JPd8UdQP8vUkweJb53EicF1icSYjOg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);background-size: 100%;background-repeat: no-repeat;background-position: right center;"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">以品牌创建和星级评定为抓手，积极推进党建工作项目化运作。依托“外企党建服务联盟”，开展多种形式的共建活动，复制、推广优秀党组织的工作经验，全面提升外企党建工作水平。</span></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;"><br  /></p><p style="font family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: medium;letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: right;"><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.5568181818181818" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dtKt6iawKSvmlia54qgDdUJic00dGgzHzd0CVraqtPaO2iceibb6JTlQNze58Rl2GbBc9a2j79ToHxk1eNzhicZGsiafg/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="176" style="height: 81px;width: 145px;"></p><p><br  /></p></section></section><p><br  /></p>
